{"tid":1269672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐著呀！] 社會運動 情緒Secrets 正式啟動！","createTime":"2019-06-30T15:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T19:14:15.000Z","uid":266510,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"962a2f3f86aca7674b0a7de1c65de89ee95bfacd","tid":1269672,"uid":266510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"Hi 各位巴打絲打<br />\n因著近日社會的惡劣情況，我同一班年輕朋友自發開了個Secret Page，比大家有個平台分享下大家的感受/思考/故事/情緒 etc，大家有需要、有興趣就入來一起分享下啦！寫又得、畫張畫又得、分享首歌都得，大家互相鼓勵，戰鬥到底！<br />\n<br />\n社會運動 情緒Secrets FB Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/savehkemotionsecret/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsavehkemotionsecret%2F&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=914e81a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/savehkemotionsecret/</a><br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n【或者，講出來，我們都會舒服一點】<br />\n<br />\n簡介：<br />\n大家好，我們是一班好希望與傷心者同行的香港人。近日，社會發生一連串關於「反送中」的事情及香港當權者回應的態度，確實令好多人，特別是有著親切感受和現場經驗的我們，感到失望、傷心、憤怨、無助。<br />\n<br />\n有人選擇了離開世界，以死亡表達訴求。但，這樣的事情，一次都嫌多；這兒的生命，一個都不能少！<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們發起這個「社會運動 情緒Secrets」Page，希望大家可以匿名（當然也可留名）分享和抒發大家心裡嘅故事／感受／想法／思考／情緒／希望。<br />\n<br />\n或者，我們可以在人與人的互動中，找到多一點前行的動力。世界或者黑得不能再黑，但手足你絕不孤單！<br />\n<br />\n敘述自己的故事和經歷，亦可能是一種自我療傷的過程，又或者，講出來，我們都會舒服一點。"},{"pid":"52438faab35bab4bd57316021f68ab6507372b3c","tid":1269672,"uid":266510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3a277ba578332dcac75432d2d103d66ac6a424","tid":1269672,"uid":266510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5164aab1c674cd04ac59703d843ecb3e80d1e3c","tid":1269672,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:07:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"68c7ea3ab31b94a408f1d8ba47649249061d0155","tid":1269672,"uid":264696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:08:52.000Z","msg":"已加<br />\n我都希望同到班學生傾計<br />\n我地做大嘅   唔訓都會幫到盡"},{"pid":"78909eb6fb14b7dc80707cb44bbf5804ecc5f7c3","tid":1269672,"uid":252854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:14:15.000Z","msg":"推"}]}